snippet.title: What is Starborne?
snippet.description:
Get to know the most ambitious PC strategy game in years.

Alpha going live on October 30th, sign up and download the game on: https://starborne.com/sovereign-space

Our community lives on Discord. We invite you to join our channel (https://discord.gg/starborne) where you can chat with players, developers and get instant answers to any questions you might have! Alliances are forming now.

--
